slow, and we want to make sure we hear from our audience as clearly as possible, so if you’ve got a moment, please <a href="https://voxmedia.iad1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_6u198y5wUE9lbpQ?External=home">take our little survey</a>! We are not going to paywall the entire site, I promise — but there are lots of other ideas floating around, and we’d like to narrow them down.</p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="relative z-10 font-polysans leading-120"><a class="text-16 leading-120 text-gray-4a shadow-underline-blurple hover:text-blurple dark:text-gray-ef dark:shadow-underline-franklin dark:hover:text-franklin" href="https://voxmedia.iad1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_6u198y5wUE9lbpQ?External=home" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">The Verge Subscription Survey</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->voxmedia.iad1.qualtrics.com<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card relative flex flex-row border-b border-solid border-gray-cc px-0 last-of-type:border-b-0 dark:border-gray-31 py-16 hover:bg-[#FBF9FF] dark:hover:bg-gray-18 max-w-container-sm last-of-type:border-b-0 md:px-10 lg:py-24"><a class="hover:shadow-underline-inherit after:absolute after:inset-0" aria-label="We do love our Half-Life, don’t we?" href="/2023/11/18/23967011/we-do-love-our-half-life-dont-we"></a><div class="w-38 relative flex min-w-[38px] flex-col md:ml-[-3px] md:items-start"><div class="absolute ml-0 w-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 134.51 284.18" width="24" height="50" class="h-50 w-24"><defs><linearGradient id="gradient43" gradientTransform="rotate(90)"><stop offset="40%" stop-color="#FF3D00"></stop><stop offset="55%" stop-color="#309875"></stop></linearGradient></defs><g id="Layer_2" data-name="Layer 2"><g id="Layer_1-2" data-name="Layer 1"><path fill="url(#gradient43)" class="cls-1" d="M110.91,165.78h0c-18-15.39-18-32,0-47.39h0a67.26,67.26,0,1,0-87.31,0h