t Protect smart smoke alarms that are showing as “offline.”</div><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10  [&amp;_a:hover]:text-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:text-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-franklin [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">Users <a href="https://www.googlenestcommunity.com/t5/Nest-Protect/Nest-Protect-P009-0-80-error/">have been reporting</a> the outage on Google’s forums since around November 15th. A <a href="https://www.googlenestcommunity.com/t5/Nest-Protect/Nest-Protect-P009-0-80-error/m-p/548848/highlight/true#M8838">Google community manager replied</a>, saying some 2nd gen Nest Protects are losing connection, and it’s working on a fix.</p><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mt-12 font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10  [&amp;_a:hover]:text-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:text-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-franklin [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">Some members have posted today that they’ve <a href="https://www.googlenestcommunity.com/t5/Nest-Protect/Nest-Protect-P009-0-80-error/m-p/549126/highlight/true#M8862">gotten the devices back online</a> but that there are <a href="https://www.googlenestcommunity.com/t5/Nest-Protect/Nest-Protect-P009-0-80-error/m-p/549156/highlight/true#M8865">still issues</a>. The <a href="https://status.nest.com/history">Nest status page</a> doesn’t reflect an outage as of this writing.</p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="relative z-10 font-polysans leading-120"><a class="text-16 leading-120 text-gray-4a shadow-underline-blurple hover:text-blurple dark:text-gray-ef dark:shadow-underline-franklin dark:hover:text-franklin" href="https://www.googlenestcommunity.com/t5/Nest-Protect/Nest-Protect-P009-0-80-error/td-p/548223" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Nest Protect P009(0.80) error</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->www.googlenestcommunity.com<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div><div data-native-ad-id="container" class="duet--content-cards--content-card hidden group relative z-10 flex flex-row items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-cc py-16 text-white first-of-type:pt-0 hover:bg-[#FBF9FF] dark:border-gray-31 dark:hover:bg-gray-18 max-w-container-sm md:px-10 lg:py-30"><div class="hidden"><div class="dynamic-native-ad-native_ad_content_link"></div></div><div class="flex items-center"><span class="duet--content-cards--content-card-group mr-20 hidden -rotate-180 border-l border-l-blurple pl-4 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:border-l-franklin dark:text-gray-bd md:block" style="writing-mode:vertical-lr;text-orientation:sideways">Advertisement</span><div class="max-w-content-block-mobile sm:w-content-block-compact sm:max-w-content-block-compact"><div class="mb-6 flex md:hidden"><span class="border-b border-b-blurple pb-4 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:border-b-franklin dark:text-gray-bd" style="writing-mode:initial;text-orientation:initial">Advertisement</span></div><h2 class="font-polysans text-20 font-bold leading-100 tracking-1 text-black dark:text-white md:text-24"><a data-native-ad-id="title" class="after:absolute after:inset-0 group-hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:group-hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/" aria-label="advertisement">Advertiser Content</a></h2><span class="flex pt-4 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-140 tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-94"><span class="mr-8" data-native-ad-id="byline"></span><a href="/" class="bg-white p-4" aria-label="advertisement"><img data-native-ad-id="logo" class="native-ad-logo max-h-[24px] max-w-