ailers">this week’s indie event</a>: <a href="/2023/11/14/23960739/an-rpg-for-organization-fans">organization RPG <em>Backpack Hero</em></a> and <a href="/2023/11/14/23960734/something-to-play-tonight">turn-based folktale <em>Howl</em></a>.</p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><section tabindex="-1" aria-label="A monster weekend for entertainment releases. carousel" class="duet--article--gallery relative overflow-hidden outline-none my-10 w-full"><div class="relative mb-10 h-[221px] bg-[#232323] md:h-[296px]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="A still image from the TV series Monarch: Legacy of Monsters." src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="relative top-1/2 mx-auto max-h-full max-w-full visible" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:contain"/><noscript><img alt="A still image from the TV series Monarch: Legacy of Monsters." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:contain" class="relative top-1/2 mx-auto max-h-full max-w-full visible" sizes="(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 744px" srcSet="https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:3840x1605/376x157/filters:focal(1920x803:1921x804):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24854720/Monarch_101_F00494F.jpg 376w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:3840x1605/384x160/filters:focal(1920x803:1921x804):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24854720/Mo