 URL. If the description is written by AI, it’ll say “AI-Generated Caption.”</p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="flex max-w-[500px] flex-row flex-wrap"><div class="w-full rounded-[3px] border border-solid border-gray-cc dark:border-gray-31"><div class="transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"><div class="fixed inset-0 h-[110vh] w-full bg-white transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out z-[-1] cursor-default opacity-0" role="button" aria-label="Close" tabindex="0"></div><div role="button" aria-label="Zoom" tabindex="0" class="visible z-30 w-full origin-center transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-zoom-in"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;padding-top:28.46946867565424%"></span><img alt="A screenshot of an AI-generated search description on Bing" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="responsive" class="rounded-sm" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/><noscript><img alt="A screenshot of an AI-generated search description on Bing" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="responsive" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover" class="rounded-sm" sizes="100vw" srcSet="https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:1261x359/376x107/filters:focal(631x180:632x181):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25093533/bing_ai_search_descriptions.png 376w, https://d