eam#team-donald-mustard">“partner”</a> at the company, AGBO, but it’s unclear exactly what he’ll be doing in the role. Mustard announced he was retiring from Epic Games <a href="/23864706/donald-mustard-leave-epic-games-retire-fortnite">in September</a>.</p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="duet--media--embed min-h-[100px] quickpost mb-0 w-full relative z-10 overflow-x-hidden md:max-w-full"></div></div></div></div><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card relative flex flex-row border-b border-solid border-gray-cc px-0 last-of-type:border-b-0 dark:border-gray-31 py-16 hover:bg-[#FBF9FF] dark:hover:bg-gray-18 max-w-container-sm last-of-type:border-b-0 md:px-10 lg:py-24"><a class="hover:shadow-underline-inherit after:absolute after:inset-0" aria-label="Windows Photos is getting background removal, too." href="/2023/11/17/23965835/windows-photos-is-getting-background-removal-too"></a><div class="w-38 relative flex min-w-[38px] flex-col md:ml-[-3px] md:items-start"><div class="absolute ml-0 w-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 134.51 284.18" width="24" height="50" class="h-50 w-24"><defs><linearGradient id="gradient21" gradientTransform="rotate(90)"><stop offset="40%" stop-color="#FFC2E7"></stop><stop offset="55%" stop-color="#5200FF"></stop></linearGradient></defs><g id="Layer_2" data-name="Layer 2"><g id="Layer_1-2" data-name="Layer 1"><path fill="url(#gradient21)" class="cls-1" d="M110.91,165.78h0c-18-15.39-18-32,0-47.39h0a67.26,67.26,0,1,0-87.31,0h0c18,15.39,18,32,0,47.39h0a67.26,67.26,0,1,0,87.31,0Z"></path></g></g></svg></div><div class="z-10 flex h-24 w-24 justify-center px-4 py-6 text-center font-polysans text-11 font-bold leading-none tracking-normal text-black">E</div><div class="z-10 mt-2 flex h-24 w-24 justify-center p-[5px] text-center text-black"><span class="flex w-full justify-center"><svg class="" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M24.1732 5.71429H17.4358C